1
00:00:01,520 --> 00:00:02,273
You're here!

2
00:00:02,900 --> 00:00:04,160
We collected this.

3
00:00:04,715 --> 00:00:06,341
Everything is fine, we made sure.

4
00:00:07,455 --> 00:00:08,161
Put it in the corner.

5
00:00:10,243 --> 00:00:11,157
Father wants to see you.

6
00:00:15,143 --> 00:00:17,066
Father, it's Jeanne and Sophie.

7
00:00:19,228 --> 00:00:20,061
Come over.

8
00:00:22,663 --> 00:00:23,193
There you are!

9
00:00:24,527 --> 00:00:27,169
I have something very serious to say.

10
00:00:27,444 --> 00:00:31,250
I assume you're doing your best,

11
00:00:32,070 --> 00:00:36,912
But we cannot accept the way you're behaving.

12
00:00:38,300 --> 00:00:39,801
We are very tolerant.

13
00:00:40,861 --> 00:00:43,625
One cannot expect too much from volunteers.

14
00:00:45,620 --> 00:00:48,519
But our reputation is at stake,

15
00:00:48,919 --> 00:00:51,186
And your behavior is unacceptable.

16
00:00:52,161 --> 00:00:53,755
We've had complaints,

17
00:00:54,830 --> 00:00:57,017
And I must say I'm having trouble

18
00:00:57,131 --> 00:00:58,695
believing what I've heard.

19
00:00:59,556 --> 00:01:04,622
I don't know what's gotten into you, But you've gone too far.

20
00:01:07,600 --> 00:01:08,159
In a word...

21
00:01:08,859 --> 00:01:11,318
We no longer want you working with us.

22
00:01:16,372 --> 00:01:18,125
You don't want our help?

23
00:01:22,157 --> 00:01:24,265
Perhaps you should see a doctor.

24
00:01:24,739 --> 00:01:26,011
What a very good idea!